title: Beyoncé Announces On Instagram She’s Pregnant With Twins « CBS Baltimore
text:
Beyoncé Announces On Instagram That She’s Pregnant With Twins February 1, 2017 2:07 PM Bey & Jay laughing in 2010. (Ronald Martinez/Getty Images) 
BALTIMORE (WJZ) — Blue Ivy Carter will be getting two new siblings this year. 
Beyonce announced on Instagram Wednesday that she is pregnant with twins. A photo posted by Beyoncé (@beyonce) on Feb 1, 2017 at 10:39am PST 
“We would like to share our love and happiness,” the singer captioned a photo of herself holding her pregnant belly. “We have been blessed two times over. We are incredibly grateful that our family will be growing by two, and we thank you for your well wishes. – The Carters”
